<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[خرخان]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">خرخان:</span> قَرْيةٌ بقومس بَيْنَ نَيْسابور والرَّي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[خرشن]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>: <span class="c2">(خَرْشَنَةُ، كخَرْذَلَةٍ)</span> :<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَهْمَلَهُ الجَماعَةُ، <span class="c2">(والشِّيْنُ مُعجمةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَهُوَ:</span> <span class="c2">(د بالرُّومِ)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ السّمعانيُّ:</span> أَظُنُّها بساحِلِ الشَّامِ، مِنْهُ عبْدُ الّلهِ بنُ عبْدِ الّلهِ الخَرْشنيُّ عَن مصعبِ بنِ ماهانَ صاحِب التوزيّ، وَعنهُ محمدُ بنُ الحَسَنِ بنِ الهَيْثمِ الهمذانيُّ بحرَّان.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[خرطن]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>: <span class="c2">(الخراطِينُ)</span> :<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>أَهْمَلَه الجَوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي التهْذيبِ:</span> <span class="c2">(دِيدانٌ)</span> طِوالٌ <span class="c2">(تُوجَدُ فِي الأَراضِي النَّدِيَّةِ)</span> وَفِي طينِ الأَنهارِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">قالَ الأطبَّاءُ:</span> <span class="c2">(مُدِرٌّ مُحَلِّلٌ مُفَتِّتٌ للحَصاةِ نافِعٌ لليَرَقانِ)</span> ودِهْنُه غايةٌ فِي تعظيمِ آلةِ الجماعِ مجرَّبٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">قالَ الأزْهرِيُّ:</span> وَلَا أَحْسبُها عربيَّة مَحْضة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وقالَ شيْخُنا،<span class="c5"> رَحِمَه الّلهُ تَعَالَى:</span> إنَّهم ذَكَروا أَنَّها ليسَ لَهَا مِن الحواسِ إلَاّ القوَّة اللَاّمِسَة.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[خرعون]</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>: (خَرْعون،<span class="c5"> بالفتْحِ:</span> قرْيةٌ بسَمَرْقَنْد.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[خركن]</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>: وخركن قَريةٌ بنَيْسابور.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[خرميثن]</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>: وخرْمَيْثَن،<span class="c5"> بالضمِّ:</span> قرْيةٌ ببُخَارى.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>